Lineo Didi Kilgrow, the wife of Popular Nigerian singer, Oladapo Daniel Oyebanjo aka D’banj has taken to social media to speak on the death of her first son. Daily Times reports that Daniel Oyebanjo III died while being left unattended at family pool. READ ALSO:  Obasanjo, others condole Dbanj over son’s death Lineo who recently gave birth to another boy wrote, “My heart will forever be missing a piece… but everyday gets better with you in it.” Daily Times gathered that Lineo and her husband D’banj welcomed their new son on Thursday, September 19, 2019, in California, USA. The couple have since been keeping him away from public eye.